title: 69-year-old pilot pays $4,000/month to live in a residential airpark: 'All I have to do is taxi out and take off'
description: Pilot Joe Sobczak's $698,000 home comes with a 3,600-square-foot airplane hangar, where he keeps a Beechcraft T-34 Mentor plane he can use to fly to SFO.

title: Beijing is 'watching closely' if Russia succeeds in Ukraine, NATO says, flagging rising China challenge
description: NATO Secretary-General Jens Stoltenberg said China is closely watching Russia's success in Ukraine, with the war's outcome likely to have major reverberations in Asia-Pacific.

title: I'm an experienced female solo traveler—here are 4 tips I use to be smart about my money on the go
description: Traveling alone can come with hidden costs, especially for women. These are the tips I use to fund my solo travels.

title: 'Unthinkable' that Russia does not pay for Ukraine's reconstruction, EU chief says
description: European Commission President Ursula von der Leyen said Saturday it would be "unthinkable" for Russia not to pay for Ukraine's reconstruction.

title: Elon Musk promised a lot with the Tesla Semi. Here's how it stacks up now that it's finally here
description: Five years after Elon Musk first announced the Tesla Semi, it's finally hitting roads. CNBC visited Frito-Lay Modesto, where PepsiCo is using the new trucks.

title: Ukraine 'weeks away' from full IMF support program, says fund chief
description: The IMF's Managing Director told CNBC Saturday that a fully-fledged program of support for Ukraine is "weeks away."
